1. *Preklinjem* te da ne odeš. (I beg you not to go.) 
2. Molim te, *preklinjem* te da me poslušaš. (Please, I beg you to listen to me.)
3. *Preklinjala* sam ga da me ostavi na miru. (I begged him to leave me alone.)
4. Nisam mogla da verujem da me je on *preklinjao*. (I couldn't believe he was begging me.)
5. *Preklinjali* smo ga dugo da se smiluje nad nama. (We begged him for a long time to have mercy on us.)